email.subject: Introducing GymX for mobile
email.html:
Dear Mr. Strong,

I hope this email finds you well. I'm writing to introduce you to GymX, a mobile app designed to help gym-goers track their workouts, set goals, and stay motivated.

A key feature of GymX is we use machine learning to identify all the workout moves.

Â If you're interested in learning more, I would be happy to provide you with a demo of the app and answer any questions you may have. Please let me know if this is something you'd be interested in.

Thank you for your time, John Smith
email.text:
Dear Mr. Strong,

I hope this email finds you well. I'm writing to introduce you to GymX, a
mobile app designed to help gym-goers track their workouts, set goals, and
stay motivated.

A key feature of GymX is we use machine learning to identify all the
workout moves.

 If you're interested in learning more, I would be happy to provide you
with a demo of the app and answer any questions you may have. Please let me
know if this is something you'd be interested in.

Thank you for your time, John Smith
